OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften wet and windy today with
OL,6,Fthe rain occasionally heavy and
OL,7,Fpersistent, especially later on this
OL,8,Fafternoon. Gales are likely with
OL,9,Fsevere gales possible in parts of
OL,10,FNorth Wales. A mild day, but feeling
OL,11,Funpleasant in the wind and rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FVery wet and windy this
OL,14,Fevening with clearer skies arriving
OL,15,Fovernight. Turning colder with a
OL,16,Fslight frost forming in rural spots
OL,17,Flater, and perhaps the odd wintry
OL,18,Fshower. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
